1. Crypto Airdrop Kya Hota Hai?
Airdrop ka matlab hai jab koi naya crypto project apne coins ya tokens muft (free) mein logon ke wallets mein bhejta hai. Ye aksar marketing ya naye project ko promote karne ke liye kiya jata hai.

2. Wallets aur Airdrops ka Connection
Aapki pichli images mein bataya gaya hai ki Hardware aur Paper Wallets airdrops ke liye sabse behtar kyun hain:

Aasaan Claim:                                         Hardware wallets (jaise Ledger ya Trezor) aur Paper wallets par airdrops ko claim karna bahut aasaan hota hai kyunki inme Private Keys ka poora control aapke paas hota hai.
Security:                                            Chunki aapka wallet offline (Cold Storage) hota hai, aap bina kisi hacking ke darr ke in muft coins ko apne wallet mein surakshit rakh sakte hain.
Exchanges vs Personal Wallets:                       Agar aapka crypto kisi exchange (Hot Wallet) par hai, toh zaroori nahi ki exchange aapko airdrop ke coins de. Lekin personal wallet mein wo hamesha aapke hote hain.


3. Airdrop Kaise Milte Hain?
Airdrops paane ke liye aksar kuch asaan kaam karne hote hain, jaise:

Kisi purane coin (jaise Bitcoin ya Ethereum) ko apne wallet mein hold karna.

Naye project ke social media tasks poore karna.

Project ki website par jakar apna Wallet Address register karna.

4. note:- Kabhi bhi airdrop claim karne ke liye kisi ko apna 8-12 word seed phrase na batayein. Asli airdrops sirf aapka public address mangte hain, secret key nahi.


